'''Just Toys Havoks''' was a Latin American League of Legends team. They were previously known as '''Havoks Gaming'''.

==History==
In January, 2015 the organization adquired {{bl|Satori}} roster and their spot to compete in the [[Latin America Cup 2015/LAN/Closing Cup/Regular Season|LAN Closing Cup]].

